  - UI:
    - Dark mode.
    - Connection Panel: "Connect" button + Status Log
    - Chat Panel: Messages area + Input + Send
  - LOGIC:
    - 1. REQUEST: navigator.bluetooth.requestDevice({ filters: [{ namePrefix: NamePrefix }], optionalServices: [Service] })
    - 2. CONNECT: server.connect()
    - 3. SERVICE: server.getPrimaryService(Service)
    - 4. DEBUG (CRITICAL):
       - If service.getCharacteristic(Char) FAILS:
       - Run service.getCharacteristics() to list ALL available UUIDs in the log
       - Throw error "Mismatch: Expected [Char] but found [List]"
